							<p class="extra-padding">Themes contain views and routes and are installed by uploading to the <a class="_pea-button">content/themes</a> directory.</p>	
							<p>-if up to day, show success, up to date, else prompt warning, will restart automatically - have button</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="_pea-document">
						<div class="_pea-row">
							<h3>Restart Application</h3>
							<p class="extra-padding">Themes contain views and routes and are installed by uploading to the <a class="_pea-button">content/themes</a> directory. <span class="_pea-color-error">WARNING: anything in config.json will override these settings</span></p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</form>
			</div>
			<div class="_pea-col-span5 _pea-pull-right">
				<h2>Theme Settings</h2>
